  "text": "Organotypic raft cultures from the keratinocyte cell line FK18B, which harbours the HPV-18 full-length genome, were established as previously described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, PHKs were transfected with the HPV-18 full-length genome (FK18B) and grown for different numbers of passages before raft-culture seeding (Steenbergen et al., 1998) .",
